  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find Petey</strong> is a hidden object game in which a total of 180 little bats are hidden across 4 unique levels. Embark on the search and find Petey on the farm, at the camp, on the sunny beach, and in the city. But beware: the search gets more challenging with each level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 hand-drawn unique levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >180 hidden Peteys</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unlockable levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hint Button that narrows down the search area – optional for those who need a little help</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Levels</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350890/extras/35c0284b29d496312483eb20ed9bf490.avif?t=1734418876\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock three additional levels by finding all hidden Peteys in each preceding level. Your progress is automatically saved, so you can continue playing at any time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hint Button</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350890/extras/bf49f543874fb31f1868ba9813cb4371.avif?t=1734418876\" width=616 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you ever get stuck, you can press the Hint Button. An animated arrow will guide you to a narrowed-down search area where a Petey is hiding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350890/extras/c885a3d66f38d1cbff6dd6e7104b00bf.avif?t=1734418876\" width=616 height=460 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find Petey</strong> is a hidden object game in which a total of 180 little bats are hidden across 4 unique levels. Embark on the search and find Petey on the farm, at the camp, on the sunny beach, and in the city. But beware: the search gets more challenging with each level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 hand-drawn unique levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >180 hidden Peteys</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 unlockable levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hint Button that narrows down the search area – optional for those who need a little help</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable Levels</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350890/extras/35c0284b29d496312483eb20ed9bf490.avif?t=1734418876\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock three additional levels by finding all hidden Peteys in each preceding level. Your progress is automatically saved, so you can continue playing at any time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hint Button</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350890/extras/bf49f543874fb31f1868ba9813cb4371.avif?t=1734418876\" width=616 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you ever get stuck, you can press the Hint Button. An animated arrow will guide you to a narrowed-down search area where a Petey is hiding.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3350890/extras/c885a3d66f38d1cbff6dd6e7104b00bf.avif?t=1734418876\" width=616 height=460 /></span></p>",
